"pid":"784d156b194280989a5a8d66518b438e61eee760","tid":1899700,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱新型肺炎對美國風險非常低<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，新型肺炎對美國造成的風險非常低，會適當增加應對疫情的資金，他又宣布由副總統彭斯負責領導應對疫情。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮舉行記者會，表示美國政府在疫情出現後採取的行動，例如限制中國旅客入境等，都有效減低疫情對美國民眾的影響。政府將向國會提出，要求撥款25億美元資金，用於治療和研發疫苗等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511118-20200227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511118-20200227.htm&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=c8846922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511118-20200227.htm&h=181696ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511118-20200227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b33dd2dcf2897f486f92a9778ea2fd25a0a2f8e2","tid":1899700,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵表示：冇事冇事，相信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cf4f5eb7b89fb9a31d447499e32dac5a21aedb","tid":1899700,"uid":131551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b33dd2dcf2897f486f92a9778ea2fd25a0a2f8e2","tid":1899700,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵表示：冇事冇事，相信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"有邊個國家唔係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d988e732c94d6350aca0226d50d0c9bc03bcad0","tid":1899700,"uid":9315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0cf4f5eb7b89fb9a31d447499e32dac5a21aedb","tid":1899700,"uid":131551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b33dd2dcf2897f486f92a9778ea2fd25a0a2f8e2","tid":1899700,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵表示：冇事冇